      "content": "精神上都這麼喜歡你了，如果不想睡你的話，感覺對你的肉體特別不尊敬",
      "length": 32,
      "addedAt": "2026-04-25T20:20:50.494Z"
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "content": "Precious things are very few in this world. That is the reason there is just one you. 在這世上珍貴的東西總是罕有，所以這世上只有一個你。 ",
      "length": 112,
      "addedAt": "2026-04-25T20:20:50.494Z"
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "content": "I love every moment spent with you, your love has touched my heart. ",
      "length": 68,
